{"type": "article", "id": 24596, "title": "这家在曼谷的星巴克，像是在顶上多搭了一个玻璃盒子", "description": "结合了当地特色和现代设计。", "date": "2016-03-29T07:14:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 4814, "name": "餐厅设计"}, {"id": 23974, "name": "曼谷"}, {"id": 25512, "name": "I Like Design Studio"}, {"id": 873, "name": "星巴克"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 191, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702160629Ki3ud247nLNfF9rX.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>据说星巴克的每一家店都不一样，至少在一些知名的旅游景区，星巴克通常会融入当地的特色做精品店设计。比如<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/4438.html\">在成都太古里结合了附近的大慈寺的建筑元素</a>，融入了火锅、蜀锦、双面绣等四川特色。而在东京新宿，<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/19802.html\">纯白色的店铺“让顾客感受到‘雪原’上的寂静”</a>。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160620l9K8Vg5WIzpSXRdY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">成都太古里星巴克</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160621MRa053n86DXUO4EL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">东京新宿星巴克</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>泰国也是有非常多星巴克的国家，<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/899.html\">据 2013 年的报告称，它拥有的店铺数量排在全球第 11 位。</a>目前有大概 169 家，其中首都曼谷有至少 50 家。</p>\n<p>最新开的一家在曼谷的星巴克就可以看到当地建筑特色和现代建筑手法的融合，由当地的建筑事务所<a href=\"http://www.ilikedesignstudio.com/project.php?pcode=33\"> I Like Design Studio</a> 修建，这是它们第一个星巴克的店铺设计。一楼有一个农舍似的三角屋顶，可以联系到传统的高脚楼。而二楼却是一个非常方正的玻璃盒子，与屋顶有些错位，很特别。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p class=\"\">两层楼几乎都是玻璃墙面，可以让这里显得很通透，有好的视线看风景。到了晚上的时候，屋子里面的灯光透出来，又能让楼上的玻璃盒子成为很明显的标志，引人注目。</p>\n<p class=\"\">在二楼玻璃墙的侧面，不忘用木头材料作为人鱼标志的底色，提醒着这里丰富的木材资源，泰国的森林覆盖率高达 25%。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160622f4IleBWxTmOHz2CY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70660522\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160623hkSI9fCul64JYHKF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.87375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160623yNmclvIbVo4wOkgL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160624XBFAPSbDCcQsqfyL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160624po16sqyctHleGzKF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.775\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160625uGIJQvONVby0Bki3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.44\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">室内用了更大面积的木材料，包括柜台、屋顶和桌椅，配合黑色的金属结构，让整体气氛较为传统。因为靠近公路和停车场，这里的一楼可以作为汽车餐厅。二楼的座位有小的隔断，可以用做聚会的地方。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160625aCwAr0k5ndHYUcbG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.47179487\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021606264TwW6lMNExCrtJDU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.45544554\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160626ibqFe763xE0ZXShl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.47569804\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021606274BqwR9jliIDFStZG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.47227926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160627Ekzd89A2orSbfWZx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160628CQN20ibvWEltJUqB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.43125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021606281GTnBe8ZxLgyMQal.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70660522\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021606294EFpUs3Pw7gIidmf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70660522\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2016/03/23/starbucks-glass-box-on-a-house/\">contemporist</a>、<a href=\"http://www.ilikedesignstudio.com/project.php?pcode=33\">I Like Design Studio</a></p>\n\n"}